    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "40. mighty men of valour, archers—(see on [361]Jud 20:16). Great strength as well as skill was requisite in ancient archery, as the bow, which was of steel, was bent by treading with the feet, and pulling the string with both hands.   ",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
